<th style="background:#b08261; color:#fee8ab; text-align:center; font-size:larger;">Scythians</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border:none; padding:0.6em 0 0 0;"><a href="/wiki/File:Scythia-Parthia_100_BC.png" class="image" title="Scythia-Parthia 100 BC.png"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ad/Scythia-Parthia_100_BC.png/300px-Scythia-Parthia_100_BC.png" width="300" height="191" border="0" /></a><br />
