</div>
<p>The Lithuanians may have also been of Scythian origin. Their religion was of similar beliefs and they remained pagans up until the 16th and 15th centuries.<sup class="noprint Template-Fact"><span title="This claim needs references to reliable sources&#160;since March 2009" style="white-space: nowrap;">[<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed" title="Wikipedia:Citation needed">citation needed</a></i>]</span></sup> <a name="Further_reading" id="Further_reading"></a></p>
