<li><a href="http://www.news.com.au/couriermail/story/0,23739,20246739-5003419,00.html" class="external text" title="http://www.news.com.au/couriermail/story/0,23739,20246739-5003419,00.html" rel="nofollow">A Scythian warrior found at a height of 2600 metres in the Altay Mountains in an intact burial mound</a> (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2006-08-25"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="08-25"><a href="/wiki/August_25" title="August 25">August 25</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/2006" title="2006">2006</a></span>)</li>
